title: Mystery Train
description: Finn and Jake get wrapped up in a high speed whodunit!

title: Pajama Pajimjams
description: Oscar pretends to be a talking pair of pajamas named "Jimjams" to make his friend Pajamas happy.

title: Return to Care-A-Lot
description: Bluster and his bad crowd invade Care-A-Lot, determined to steal the Care-O-Meter and stop the Care Bears' mission of caring and sharing. To foil his plan, the Bears must rely on an unlikely ally.

title: Body Adventure
description: When Cyborg is sick, Robin insists on shrinking to cell size to fight Cyborg's infection himself.

title: Please and Thank You Song
description: Mei goes around the farm with food for the animals. She offers them some food and the animals say "yes please"

title: The Little Mer-Tiger
description: The origin of Tiger is told as a flashback.  As the legend goes, Tiger used to be a mermaid.  One day the evil ruler of the sea, Bubble Grandpa, demanded a hamburger and picked Tiger to retrieve it.  He used his magic sea powers to give Tiger legs and send her ashore.  But Tiger grew to love the land, and with the help of her new friend, Uncle Grandpa, defeated the evil sea ruler and got to keep her legs.

title: Be Afraid of the Dark
description: Ben travels into space to thwart Ghostfreak's diabolical plans. But is he hero enough to take on the Mummy, Werewolf and Frankenstein?

title: Coffee Cave
description: After finding out Ice Bear is a master barista, the Bears turn their cave into a popular coffee shop. But it all goes awry when Ice Bear gets too into coffee and goes berserk.

title: MacBarm's Day Off/Playhouse Problems
description: It's MacBarm's day off and Zee takes over harvesting carrots with his Zee mobile, but when it breaks, the work still needs to be done./Ranger Nat is bringing a playhouse on the train for Timmy and Izzy, but it won't fit through the tunnel!

title: Haunted Campfire
description: The campers must battle ghosts of their own creation after their scary stories mysteriously come true.

title: Guardians of Sunshine
description: Finn and Jake go into BMO to defeat an evil Big Boss.

title: Blukic and Driba Go to Mr. Smoothy's
description: The Plumbers' resident geniuses, Blukic and Driba set off to find some smoothies meanwhile Ben and Rook try to stop Trombipulor from gaining the source of absolute power.

title: Christmas Scavenger Hunt
description: Blippi wonders what is the best part about Christmas?

title: The Library
description: The campers spend a rainy day at the library.

title: Moon Problems
description: The Moon gets sad when Oscar loses his friendship bracelet.

title: Death in Bloom
description: Finn and Jake are terrible house sitters and have to go on a quest to replace Princess Bubblegum's rare flower.

title: The Curse of Elmore
description: When Gumball's schoolfriend Leslie finds an old video tape, the creepy mystery of Elmore's ghostly past unfolds. Featuring spooky and hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Big Trip
description: It's time for the gang's yearly vacation, but Hawk refuses to go, claiming the gang's vacations are never fun for him because the others are terrible at vacationing. Hawk only agrees to go if the gang pass his super-intense vacation training course.

title: Puff Paint
description: Oscar's painting is unpopular so he goes on a journey of self-discovery.

title: Pajamas Party
description: When Pajamas starts to panic that Oscar will outgrow her, Oscar tries to help but things go awry.

title: Reststop Roustabout
description: With the Rustbucket stopped on the Midwest roadside, Ben locks himself inside with his tablet as Max and Gwen enjoy the great outdoors, until Team Tennyson is pulled into a wild Jack-a-Lope chase.

title: Director's Cut
description: Oscar receives a camcorder from his parents and sets out to prove to them the magic on the island is real.

title: Sneakerheads
description: Apple & Onion need a Last Will and Testament if they are to protect their belongings from the state.

title: El Futuro
description: Steven por fin está listo para avanzar.

title: Classic Rock
description: Batman thinks he's helping a homeless old man who is being mugged on the street only to discover that the man is a powerful wizard being chased by demons in disguise. It turns out the wizard is on a mission to save Shazam from the clutches of Black Adam.

title: The Sound and the Furry
description: As Team Tennyson leaves the Frozen Man Festival, Lord Decibel takes center stage to threaten the festival-goers, creating an avalanche if his ransom isn't paid. An over matched Ben must step out of his comfort zone to save the festival from his noisy nemesis!

title: The Beepers: The Visitor
description: The Beepers find the perfect groove after a new friend shreds a little too hard.

title: Time Traveling Quick Pants
description: Oscar and Hedgehog learn about a quicksand that lets them go back in time.

title: Cosmic Bupkiss
description: A storm blocks Oscar and Hedgehog's one chance to see a comet.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Dumbrella
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, have been traveling on the back of a truck in the rain for days. Charlie produces an umbrella to help his friend but unfortunately it's a "dumbrella" and it's looking to have some fun with them!

title: Fragments
description: Steven heads to the woods to train with a powerful mentor.

title: El gran viaje
description: Es hora de las vacaciones anuales de la banda, pero Halcondrilo se niega a ir, alegando que las vacaciones de la banda nunca son divertidas para él porque los otros son pésimos compañeros de vacaciones. De hecho, Halcondrilo solo acepta ir si la banda aprueba su curso de entrenamiento de vacaciones superintensivo: ilos desafíos temáticos más emocionantes que se puedan imaginar!

title: Elmore's Most Wanted
description: Gumball's dad has been revealed as "Elmore's Most Wanted" - but when the Chief of Police tries to investigate, things do not go according to plan. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Career Day
description: After an excessive spending spree, the Golden Goose tells the gang it won't give them any more golden eggs until they learn the value of money. Following Rick's advice to save money, the gang open a cookie shop to make money on their own and save it in a huge vault.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Planet Bears
description: A nature documentary follows the Bears through their normal routine, which includes a trip to the grocery store.

title: The Big Freeze
description: The Bears investigate the mysterious transformation of a tropical valley into a winter wonderland of snow. To return it to its natural state, Funshine must follow Dibble's example and give up something he wanted for himself.

title: Snowy Excavator Song
description: A special animated music video episode to the tune of Blippi's new "Snowy Excavator" Song.

title: Monster Visit
description: The monsters get nervous when their Godmonster comes for a visit.

title: Twelve Angry Hedgehogs
description: Hedgehog wants to win the Golden Science Badge but runs into some unexpected competition.

title: Safari Sa'Bad
description: On their trip to Adrenaworld West, Ben takes a detour on a jungle cruise and finds himself hunted by the evil Tim Buktu. Our hero must outwit the baddie if he wants to make it off the amusement park ride alive!

title: Late Night Talky Time
description: The moon is bored of taking the nightshift, since everyone's always asleep. So Unikitty leads the gang in putting on an over-the-top late night talk show to keep the moon occupied.

title: Everything's Fine
description: Steven insists that everything is fine.

title: Ninjago Confidential
description: Back in Ninjago City, Zane and Pixal hit the mean streets to track down Milton Dyer, only to discover that things are not what they seem.

title: Snow-verload
description: The Bears investigate the mysterious transformation of a tropical valley into a winter wonderland of snow. To return it to its natural state, Funshine must follow Dibble's example and give up something he wanted for himself, just as Bluster and his bad crowd invade Care-A-Lot! They're determined to steal the Care-O-Meter and stop the Care Bears' mission of caring and sharing. To foil his plan, the Bears must rely on an unlikely ally.

title: Back to the Library
description: Uncle Grandpa uses time travel to convince his past self to return a library book on time.

title: Classroom
description: Over the course of a single day in Ms. Baker's class, we see how Clarence and his classmates deal with their individual trials during the school day.

title: Ralph
description: Charlie meets a creature just like him named Ralph. Charlie loves having a new friend, but the Bears think Ralph is bad news.

title: The Hero
description: Gumball and Darwin are determined to prove to their dad that he is their hero, at any cost!

title: The Powerpuff Girls: A Documentary/Girls Gone Mild
description: The Powerpuff Girls a Documentary: A film student attempts to do a documentary on the Powerpuff Girls and learns catching these superheroes at rest is harder than he thought./Girls Gone Mild: When Parents Against Powerpuffs tell the girls that their superheroics are becoming too imitable, the girls must hold back on fighting crime.

title: Ninjago Confidencial
description: De vuelta en la ciudad de Ninjago, Zane y Pixal salen a las calles para encontrar a Milton Dyer, y descubren que las cosas no son lo que parecen…

title: Game Time
description: Chef Hector hires The Looney Builders to build him a burger restaurant, but Daffy is so focused on beating his handheld game that he causes major setbacks.

title: Space Invasion
description: A visit from Puddle the alien tests the limit of Oscar's hosting skills.

title: Pepper's Blanket Is Missing
description: Pepper's blanket goes missing at a cabin sleepover.

title: Ticking Crime Bomb
description: Leshawna and Izzy trick Owen into thinking he's destined to be a criminal mastermind, but when he leaves school to join the scariest gang in town, they have to mount a rescue attempt.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Fuzzy Pink Time Babies
description: Oscar and Hedgehog learn how to stop time.

title: Ruidosos y Peludos
description: Cuando los Tennyson se van del Festival Frozen Man, Lord Decibel ocupa el escenario central para amenazar a los asistentes y crear una avalancha si no pagan el rescate que pide. iBen se ve superado por su rival y debe salir de su zona de confort para salvar al festival de su entrometido enemigo!

title: A Lot Like Lola
description: Lola wants everyone to be more like her until they all start acting exactly like her.

title: Space Race
description: With Clarence distracted by the mysterious power of the moon, his class competes to build the highest-flying rocket. Will Sumo's homemade bucket of bolts beat Belson's store-bought rocket?

title: The Dream
description: When Gumball blames Darwin for kissing Penny in his dream it threatens to tear apart their friendship, the only place you can fix a dream problem is in the dream world.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Big City Dancers
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, traveling on the back of a truck visit NYC where the rhythms of the city make Charlie wanna dance his little back porch off. Frank … not so much. But when you go far enough into the city, anything can happen.

title: Mop Forever
description: At Alice's dress-up party the campers are magically turned into their costumes.

title: Kana Recharges
description: Tired and in need of relaxation, Kana decides to take a well-deserved break between deliveries. When she tells Thomas that she wants time all by herself, Thomas is worried that he and the other engines have done something to upset her. Determined to right their assumed wrongs, Thomas and friends follow Kana around the island to convince her to play with them -- the exact opposite of what she needs! When a big storm reaches Sodor, Kana teaches her friends about the value of spending time alone and "feeling the hush."
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Garbage Truck
description: Blippi and TABBS shrink down and fly into a garbage truck where they meet Horace, a singing and dancing fly, who shows them what he loves to eat--garbage!

title: Computer Vampire
description: Oscar finds a mysterious old video game in the library.

title: Road Trip
description: A road trip in Cyborg's T-Car is really fun - for a while.

title: Feeling Spacey
description: Oscar and Hedgehog arrive on a planet that has no emotions.

title: We Baby Bears: BHA Bha Song
description: We Baby Bears follows baby bear brothers Grizz, Panda, and Ice Bear as they journey in a magical box to fantastic different worlds in search of their perfect home.

title: Lighthouse
description: The Bears find a lighthouse powered by a luminous creature.

title: Doll's House
description: The Bears apply to be roommates in a fantastic dream dollhouse.

title: Australia Kangaroo
description: Blippi stumbles across a Kangaroo Crossing sign in Australia and wonders "How high can a kangaroo jump?" His new kangaroo mate Rudy is happy to demonstrate, challenging Blippi to a hopping race around the famous sandstone monolith Uluru. Can Blippi jump as high as a kangaroo?

title: I Am My Monster
description: Everything is not fine.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Song of Sodor
description: When Nia suggests adding a song to spice up Sir Topham Hatt's new bench unveiling, he calls upon her to write a song for the ceremony, but Nia soon finds she may have bitten off more than she can sing.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: The First Day
description: Best friends Oscar and Hedgehog get dropped off at their first day at summer camp.

title: Cool Bikes
description: Mordecai and Rigby want cool bikes because if their bikes are cool, then they are cool.

title: Asteroid Blues
description: An asteroid is headed right for the kingdom, so Dr Fox leads the gang on a mission to save the kingdom by flying a rocket to the asteroid's surface and blowing it to bits with a huge bomb. But when they get there the gang finds the lonely asteroid is actually a super nice guy and don't want to blow him up.

title: Ancients of the Creek
description: Craig, Kelsey and JP discover an ancient fort that belonged to the first kids in the Creek.

title: The Prodigal Father
description: Zane, kidnapped by the Mechanic, faces Unagami. Master Wu fights to free Zane, while Pixal questions Milton Dyer for information on how to shut down Prime Empire.

title: Soy Mi Monstruo
description: No todo está bien.

title: Follow that Space Cab!
description: While Superman escorts his prisoner Mr. Mind between planets, he is attacked by Lobo who wants to collect a reward on Mind. Temporarily powered-down, Superman seeks Space Cabbie's help to get away from Lobo.

title: The Pony
description: Gumball and Darwin race home to spend quality time with Anais, but every likely obstacle gets in way... and some unlikely ones too!

title: Night of the Bat
description: Superman and other Justice League members have to battle Batman when he gets possessed by an evil Djinn, Uthool, who is intent on using the JL power core to blow a crack in Earth.

title: The Beepers: Funky Time
description: The Beepers play with tempo and learn that adapting to change can be…sweaty.

title: Popular Banana Split
description: Hedgehog and Max discover a tiny high school when they are accidentally shrunk by a science experiment.

title: Secret in a Bottle
description: Craig needs to get a secret off his chest, so he pays a visit to the Keeper of Secrets in the Creek.

title: Mother's Day Madness
description: The babies compete to see who can create the best Mother's Day card.

title: Homeworld Bound
description: Steven heads to the Diamonds for advice on how to control his new powers.

title: Same Old World
description: Steven flies around the world.

description: Our ninja barely have time to mourn the loss of their fallen ninja friends before being thrust into the madness of Terra Domina where Lloyd will have to face an old adversary from his past.

title: Alpha Bodies
description: Cartoonito presents Alpha Bodies! It's time to use our bodies to make every letter of the alphabet, from A to Z, but one over-eager letter keeps getting ahead of itself.

description: Mordecai needs access to the computer so he and Rigby challenge Muscle Man and High Five Ghost to a basketball game for a week's worth of computer time.

title: Chocolate Money Badgers
description: Oscar learns that he can earn merit badges that unlock prizes.

title: The Substitute
description: After Ms. Baker takes an unexpected personal day, she is replaced by a substitute that has a hard time handling the unruly classroom. Soon, the school day devolves into chaos and it is up to Clarence to get Mrs. Baker back to where she belongs, the classroom.

title: Log Date 7 15 2
description: Steven sneaks a listen to a friend's audio diary.

title: Pee Pee G's/Boy Toys
description: The Pee Pee G's: When the girls wake up to discover their bed is wet, none of them want to admit that they are the guilty party./Boy Toys: The girls allow Princess to become a Powerpuff Girl when they realize they need help trying to defeat the Rowdyruff Boys.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Rap It Up
description: Mordecai and Rigby don't want Pops to be called a loser so they say that they'll join him in a rap battle.

title: The Opening Act
description: After failing to open a jar Chef believes he's past his prime and entering his twilight years. This prompts Beth and the kids to dig up something from his youth to rejuvenate him. That something turns out to be a ventriloquist dummy named Sue.

title: Vote Gumball…and Penny?
description: Gumball is running for School President and is looking for a worthy running mate. When he asks his girlfriend Penny, he does not get the answer he expects. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Mother's Day
description: Gumball, Darwin and Anais need to find the perfect Mother's Day gift. Will it be a cute card, a thoughtful painting or something entirely different? Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Soundhouse
description: Oscar and Hedgehog discover a new structure on the island and become friends with its caretaker.

title: Find Your Bliss
description: When Bubbles blames a string of accidents on her imaginary friend Bliss, her sisters begin to think she's lost her mind.

title: Professor Lampwick
description: Chloe's professor is too mean to give her any face time to talk over her poor grade. The Bears take things into their own hands to help, causing big trouble for Chloe.

title: Wash Your Hands, Scrub That Soap
description: Ella is getting muddy. Mei comes out with a plate of dumplings, but Ella's hands are dirty!

title: I Heart Heartforde
description: Oscar, hedgehog and the other campers are excited to take a trip to the non-magical town of Heartforde.

title: Knit Wit
description: Duncan tries to hide his newfound secret power: kitting. But after using it to save his classmates he proudly admits it.

title: Campers Above the Bed
description: Hedgehog finds a city underneath her bed as she looks for her missing diary.

title: King Gus
description: Things get out of hand when Mr. Gus fulfills a timeless legend and is deemed king of the food court.

title: Camping Can Be Cool
description: Mordecai tries to prove to Margaret that camping is cool.

title: Boys vs Girls
description: The Titans try to settle the eternal question: Are boys or girls better?

title: Many Happy Returns
description: Gwen and Kevin pay Ben a surprise visit, but does Kevin's strange behavior have anything to do with an angry Tetramand princess, or her father's fleet of warships prepared to attack the Earth?

title: Salad Salsa
description: Mei, Ella, animals cook a delicious salad using local vegetables

title: Abate and Switch
description: When the JLA tries to stop the Brothers Djinn, the ghoulish trio are able to direct spells on our heroes by saying their names forcing them to disguise themselves as each other in order to foil the spells.

title: Ice Cream Headache
description: The campers get magical powers from the witches supply of magic ice cream.

title: The Last Laugh
description: Disappointed when his friends don't laugh at his jokes, Funshine encounters the Laffinpuff, a magical comedian who grants Funshine's wish to make everyone think he's funny. But Funshine realizes it's no fun being funny when people laugh at everything he says, whether he means it to be funny or not. To get the wish rescinded, he must face the Laffinpuff in a grueling ordeal of slapstick humor.

title: Grass is Greener
description: MOE wants to know what it's like to be a member of the Batwheels, but the bot gets more than he bargained for when Bam invites him along for an exciting mission to stop Poison Ivy.

title: Malefactor
description: Khyber and his dog attacks Ben and Rook while they're at the "Olde Bellwood Days" festival, but does the hunter have other plans? (Introducing new Nemetrix alien Hypnotick.)

title: Hello Around the World
description: Cartoonito presents Hello Around the World! All across the globe, friends greet each other in lots of different languages. Watch along and discover some of the many ways to say "Hello," around the world and beyond!

title: El Padre Prodigo
description: Zane, secuestrado por el Mecánico mientras Pixal interroga a Milton Dyer para obtener información sobre cómo cerrar el Primer Imperio.

title: Ballroom
description: MG fixes up the ballroom and warns UG and PS not to step a foot in there until he gets a chance to use it.  But UG mistakenly tosses a ball into the room.  Now PS and UG have to retrieve the ball without touching one foot to the ground.

title: The Visitor
description: A mysterious alien named Xylene shows up and wants to return the Omnitrix to its rightful owner, Grandpa Max!

title: Lame Station
description: Pizza Steve tries desperately to make the others in the RV interested in his new game console.

title: The Beepers: Spotlight
description: When a spotlight gives everyone a chance to solo, a shy Beeper discovers the courage to shine.

title: Breaking Bliss
description: When Bliss struggles to control her powers an evil force arises to take advantage.

title: The Sidekick
description: During a quest to retrieve a loaned video game, Darwin begins to suspect that he is trapped playing second fiddle to Gumball.

title: The Real You
description: Finn has to give a speech at Princess Bubblegum's science barbecue and seeks out a quick fix to make himself smarter.

title: Juego Terminado
description: Unagami entra al mundo real y aterroriza a la ciudad de Ninjago mientras Jay, Zane y Pixal intentan evitar el desastre reuniendo a Unagami con Dyer.

title: CN Special: NBA All-Star Slam Dunk Contest
description: Cartoon Network's version of the NBA Slam Dunk Contest, highlighting the best slam dunks, hosted by the Teen Titans.

title: Van Hogling
description: Chef and the kids take a field trip to Sugar's farm but ignoring all of Sugar's strict and boring farm rules have dire consequences when Chef and the kids unleash a herd of ravenous "Were-hogs" on a full moon.

title: Jeff's Secret
description: When Clarence discovers a new quirk about his friend, Jeff begs Clarence not to tell. Can Clarence resist the urge to expose Jeff's secret to the whole school?

title: Barn Mates
description: Steven helps two friends get along at the barn.

title: Falafel's Car Keys
description: Apple & Onion are deemed responsible enough to borrow Falafel's car for their first road trip together. Nothing will go wrong, and they're going to make sure of that… by getting some practice in.

title: Susie's Fantastical Scavenger Hunt
description: Oscar and Hedgehog must learn to exist without each other when they are put on different teams during a scavenger hunt.

title: House Rules
description: Mordecai and Rigby are sick of Benson's house rules and want to live without them.

title: Saxophone Come Home
description: Oscar befriends a teenage Yeti.

title: Takers Keepers
description: Daffy steals Taz's favorite toy but he learns you can't just take everything you want.

title: Welcome to the Unikingdom
description: After Unikitty finds out that tourism is down in the Unikingdom, she recruits the gang to make a tourism video to inspire people to visit the kingdom. But after calamities come one after another, Unikitty begins to think the video is going to turn out to be a disaster. However the friends save the day with some creativity and manage to get a single tourist to visit. Mission accomplished!

title: Virtual Reality Bites
description: When the school switches to virtual reality, Harold uses the opportunity to get the respect he feels he rightfully deserves.

title: El Templo de la Locura
description: Jay debe enfrentarse solo a Unagami en el juego final, pero Unagami tiene una batalla más grande al enfrentarse a la verdad sobre su propia identidad.

title: Dullance
description: Burned out from having so many adventures, Clarence struggles to sit around and do nothing.

title: Blisster Sister
description: The Girls hang out with their new big sister Bliss, who gets a taste of fighting bad guys as part of the Powerpuff Girls.

title: The Boys Are Back in Town
description: Him brings the Rowdyruff Boys back, protecting them from the girls' feminine wiles.

title: Skiff Sails Sodor
description: When Skiff gets a crack in his hull, Thomas needs to move him overland to Harwick for repairs, but Skiff's land-sickness makes that challenging.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Detenerse, Caer y Girar
description: Los Ninjas no han ni llorado la pérdida de sus amigos  caídos cuando ya deben entrar a la locura de Tierra Domina.

title: Bubble Fields
description: The Bears try to prove to Unica that they can be expert bubble-ologists.

title: That's the Stuff
description: While touring a space museum, Ben's excitement multiplies when he learns that recently discovered space stuff is being examined inside the museum's lab. Once the stuff comes to life and the shape-shifting goo replicates our hero, Ben must look within if he is to stop the case of mistaken identity.

title: Los Safaris son Malos
description: En su paseo a Adrenaworld West, Ben toma un desvío por una selva y descubre que lo persigue el malvado Tim Buktu. iNuestro héroe debe ser más listo que el villano si quiere llegar al parque de diversiones con vida!

title: Wide Load Vacay: Eye Spy
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, are traveling on the back of a truck from Montana to Utah. Charlie wants to play a game of Eye Spy. He finds more and more obvious objects for Frank to spy but Frank isn't quite getting the hang of it. Yet!

title: Eyesore a Sunset
description: Art is subjective and Apple and Onion agree to let that get between them.

title: The Future
description: Steven is finally ready to move on.

title: In the Darkness/Indecisive Emily
description: An encounter with Storm and his trick rose leaves Magnus temporarily blinded and unable to brawl. With the help of an unlikely partner, Magnus pursues Storm in an attempt to defeat him and restore his vision./ Emily obtains a second Bakugan named Chrissy. It's soon obvious that Emily is having trouble brawling with both Chrissy and Webam, and it's up to Dan, Drago and Gillator to teach them how to brawl as a team.

title: Crisis at Elder Rock
description: Tragedy strikes the Creek when the Elders get trapped under Elder Rock, and it's up to Craig, Kelsey and JP to rescue them.

title: Mr. Softball
description: Susie challenges the campers to a game of softball to get out of doing a chore.

title: Recycle Stomp
description: Mei, the children and some animals are in the park collecting trash to recycle!

title: The Basketball Liaries
description: With the help from Basketball, Oscar makes an impressive shot that scores him a spot on the Gold League.

title: Momsoon
description: Hedgehog gets a call during her radio show from someone who needs her help.

title: Asteroide Triste
description: Un asteroide viaja directo hacia el reino, por lo que la Dra. Fox se pone al frente de la banda en una misión para volar en un cohete hasta la superficie del asteroide y hacerlo explotar en pedazos con una enorme bomba para así salvar el reino. Pero al llegar, la banda descubre que el asteroide solitario es en realidad un tipo sumamente agradable y se rehúsan a hacerlo explotar. Por desgracia, el asteroide se entera del plan de Fox y sale corriendo llorando, icon la bomba aún en su interior! La Dra. Fox, arrepentida, lleva de urgencia a la banda tras el asteroide para levantarle el ánimo antes de que sea demasiado tarde.

title: Rumbo al Planeta Madre
description: Steven acude a las Diamantes para pedirles consejos sobre cómo controlar sus nuevos poderes.

title: Lowlifes
description: Apple & Onion cannot allow themselves to be viewed by society- and more importantly by smug old Chicken Nugget-as lowlifes.

title: The Temple of Madness
description: Jay must stand alone against Unagami in the end-game, yet Unagami has a bigger battle in facing the truth about his own identity.

title: Say What?
description: When Share magically has her voice stolen from her in a field of flowers, she and the other Bears must learn to listen so they can find her voice and solve the problem between the flowers and their Whiffle gardeners.

title: The Best Robin
description: When the other Titans are too lazy to fight Brother Blood, Robin calls on his secondary team: Team Robin, a crime-fighting group made up of different Robins.

title: The Eclipse/Follow Haavik!
description: There's an eclipse happening over Los Volmos, but there's something even more strange going on. Dan and Drago quickly realize something's up; no one seems like themselves today. The two need to get to the bottom of it and return things back to normal./ Magnus and Ajit spot Haavik on the street and decide to follow him, but the shape shifting Haavik is on to them. It's not long before an epic brawl breaks out between them - Five Faction Fusion Sabrus vs. Nillious X Darkus and Pharol.

title: Susan Strong
description: Finn and Jake meet some humans living underground. Except, they find the Candy People irresistible.

title: Susie Appreciation Day
description: Hedgehog and Oscar find themselves trapped in Susie's cabin and must escape undetected.

title: It's My Party
description: Oscar and Hedgehog plan a surprise birthday party for Susie.

title: Mortimor to the Rescue
description: When Craig, Kelsey and JP get stranded in murky water, it's up to Mortimor to save the day!

title: Outbreak
description: When Dr. Psychobos steals a part out of the Omnitrix, causing chaotic side effects, it's up to Ben, Rook, and a small team of Plumbers get everything back to normal. (Introducing new Ben alien Kickin' Hawk, temp Ben alien Walkatrout, Upchuck Rook.)

title: Super Watermelon Island
description: Steven finds out what happened to all those sentient watermelons he created.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Dia de profesionales
description: Después de un gasto excesivo, Golden Goose le dice a la pandilla que no les dará más huevos de oro hasta que aprendan el valor del dinero. Siguiendo el consejo de Rick de ahorrar dinero, la pandilla abrió una tienda de galletas para ganar dinero por su cuenta y guardarla en una gran bóveda.

title: Wheels on the Bus
description: Ella and Mummy take the big red bus to Lellobee farm, where she meets Mia and the rest of the team!

title: Game Over
description: Unagami breaks into the real world and terrorizes Ninjago City while Jay, Zane and Pixal attempt to prevent disaster by reuniting Unagami with his creator, Milton Dyer.

title: Puddle Olympics
description: The kids take turns jumping over a puddle but Sylvester is afraid of the water.

title: Batcomputer for a Day
description: When Batcomputer shuts down for a system update, the other Batwheels must take over for her while aiding Batman in a battle against Harley Quinn.

title: Back to Our Regular Time Period
description: The Bears find themselves trapped in the wrong time period.

title: To Tell the Tooth
description: When Bugs loses a baby tooth, Daffy tries to figure out how to scam the tooth fairy.

title: Hedgehog Werewolf
description: Hedgehog gets bit by a cute puppy and is starting to act strange.

title: Ghost the Boy
description: Oscar and Hedgehog befriend a ghost who can't remember who he is.

title: A New View for Thomas
description: When Thomas spends the day carrying rockstar idol Harold across Sodor, he gains a new perspective on just how amazing it is to be his engine-self.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: The Secret of the Omnitrix Part 1
description: In a battle with Animo, Ben in hero mode, doesn't listen to reason from Max and Gwen, and gets engulfed in a weird energy light. Little does Ben know that the "self destruct" function on the Omnitrix has just been initiated!

title: Sneeze Guard
description: Oscar and Hedgehog must work with the witches to cure Alice's camp-threatening illness.

title: Todo Esta Bien
description: Steven insiste en que todo está bien.

title: Radio Silence
description: Oscar must get Hedgehog a special sandwich in order to save their friendship.

title: The Big Skunk Funk
description: Abuzz with excitement about the Sodor Flower Festival, Thomas is given the important task of transporting Sir Topham Hatt's prized roses to the event. On the way, Thomas' sweet-smelling journey takes a turn for the stinky when a skunk crosses the tracks and sprays the engine with the funkiest scent imaginable! Now, with the help of his friends, Thomas must find a way to get rid of the stench and get to the festival on time.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Charlie's Big Foot
description: After Charlie hurts his foot, The Bears have to sneak him into a hospital for medical assistance.

title: The Great Elf Invention Convention
description: Oscar, Max, and Hedgehog do a favor for Barb the elf in exchange for some chips.

title: The Storm
description: Love is in the air and Gumball is caught in the center of an emotional hurricane - literally!

title: Oscar & Hedgehog's Melody
description: Susie holds the annual talent show that has the rest of the campers competing to win.

title: Fragmentos
description: Steven se dirige al bosque para entrenarse con un poderoso mentor.

title: The Unnaturals
description: Ben learns that evil robots have replaced all the kids at the Little League World Series. And now they want to replace the President of the USA!

title: Gem Drill
description: Steven takes a journey deep underground.

title: Power Outage
description: A ghoul known as Calythos possesses the Parasite in order to drain the Justice League of its powers and use that stolen strength to open a massive volcano.

title: Filthy Rich
description: What does it take to be truly content? Whatever it takes, Apple and Onion are going to achieve it.

title: Mouth Hole
description: Robin goes on a quest to gain a new power: whistling.

title: Charlas Nocturnas
description: La luna está aburrida de tomar el turno de noche, ya que todos siempre están dormidos. Entonces, Unikitty lidera a la pandilla en la presentación de un programa de entrevistas nocturno exagerado para mantener la luna ocupada.

title: Trading Day
description: After Craig accidentally destroys a shipment of rare Chocorolls at the Trading Tree, Kit makes him work off his debt by running her trades throughout the Creek!

title: Lying Around the House/Bubble Boy
description: Lying Around The House: The girls tell little white lies that turn into a big, bad problem./Bubble Boy: Realizing that the only way to beat the Rowdyruff Boys is to join them, Bubbles takes Boomer's place in this rough-and-tumble band of boys.

title: The AB Bakugan Battle League!
description: With all the mayhem and destruction Haavik is causing, the Awesome Brawlers decide that a bit of Bakugan brawling is the perfect distraction to take their minds off all the trouble. With the help of some friends, they start the Awesome Brawler Bakugan Battle league!/ The Awesome Brawler's Bakugan Battle league rages on. Just as the semifinal round comes to a close, an uninvited guest crashes the party, bringing an alarming end to the battle league.

title: Spiderweb
description: A gorgeous spider web in the park has Blippi wondering "How do spiders make their webs?" He sets off to find the answer! A very talented spider explains the artistic process and Blippi is surprised by the masterful picture that ends up in the spiders' web!

title: Bridezilla
description: When Mojo and Barbarus announce their wedding, the girls are convinced that they're up to no good.

title: La Naturaleza de las Cosas
description: Mientras pasean por el Parque Nacional Geyser Gulch, el trío Tennyson descubre un generador a vapor de Steam Smyth y debe apagarlo antes de que sobrecargue la red eléctrica o, peor, icause un terremoto masivo que destruya el parque entero!

title: Es la cosa
description: Mientras visita un museo espacial, la emoción de Ben se multiplica cuando se entera de que están examinando en el laboratorio unas "cosas espaciales" que acaban de descubrir. Pero cuando esa cosa viscosa cobra vida y comienza a replicar a nuestro héroe con su capacidad de cambiar de forma, Ben debe buscar en su interior si quiere detener el caso de identidad equivocada.

title: The Return
description: Ghostfreak has returned! And he has brought a Mummy, Werewolf and Frankenstein like aliens with him to help him shroud the Earth in darkness.

title: Parada de Descanso
description: Con el Rustbucket detenido en la carretera del Medio Oeste, Ben se encierra con su tablet mientras que Max y Gwen disfrutan del hermoso paisaje, hasta que el equipo Tennyson debe involucrarse en una persecución salvaje de un jackalope.

title: Bienvenidos al Unireino
description: Después de descubrir que el turismo escasea en el Unireino, Unikitty recluta a la banda para que hagan un video que inspire a la gente a visitar el reino. Pero luego de varias calamidades, Unikitty comienza a creer que el video resultará siendo un desastre. Sin embargo, los amigos salvan el día con algo de creatividad y logran hacer que un solo turista los visite. iMisión cumplida!

title: Seed No Evil/City of Clipsville
description: Seed No Evil: When a prehistoric caveman thaws out in Townsville, the girls must stop him from stealing the Mayor's seeds./City of Clipsville: The girls reminisce on their adventures in these new, never-before-seen clips!

title: Silly Hat Catastrophe!/Zee In A Bottle
description: Lloyd is selling silly hats at the factory, but when the hat machine malfunctions it starts raining silly hats on Pretty Big City!/Zee makes a giant rocket ship in a bottle, but things take a turn when he gets stuck inside!

title: Tiko's Back?!/Arise, Ultimate Infinity!
description: Tiko's Back?!: In order to make Sabrus a 6 faction fusion Bakugan, Haavik heads into the maze to try to capture a golden Bakugan who has brought "mayhem and destruction" to Earth once before - Tiko!/Arise, Ultimate Infinity!: The Awesome Brawlers manage to thwart Haavik's attempt to fuse Tiko with Sabrus, but Haavik ends up escaping with the golden Bakugan, Pyravian. Now the Awesome Brawlers must track down Haavik before he can form his ultimate 6 faction fusion Bakugan.

title: Monster Babies
description: Alice lures Oscar and his monster friends for a tea party, but only to turn the monsters into cute babies.

title: Gone Fishin'
description: When their fishing trip in Undertown takes a bizarre twist, Ben, Rook, and Grandpa Max, begin their search for a ship-bottling alien pirate who has captured Magister Patelliday. (Introducing Capt. Cork.)

title: Ancestor Act
description: When Gumball's sister Anais researches the Watterson family tree, she uncovers a long history of nonsense. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Midnight Quittance
description: Ramona invites Hedgehog and Oscar to participate in a special holiday ritual.

title: Spell Crushers
description: Hedgehog tries to get over a crush so she can regain her focus on magic.

title: Bath on the Nile
description: The Bears find themselves in an ancient Egyptian spa, but Grizz refuses to take a bath.

title: Bliss Reminisce
description: The Girls learn Bliss' backstory from the Professor, Mojo Jojo, and Bliss herself.

title: Haavik's Challenge/Storm Haavik's Tower
description: Haavik's Challenge: Haavik has crashed the Awesome Brawlers Bakugan League, and challenges the Awesome Brawlers in a battle league of his own!/ Storm Haavik's Tower: In order to keep Earth and Vestroia safe and rescue Drago, the Awesome Brawlers agree to enter Haavik's Bakugan Battle League, and race toward Haavik's tower for the final showdown.

title: Beach Battle
description: When The Looney Builders enter a sandcastle building contest, Tweety sees the competition and loses confidence in his idea.

title: The Nature of Things
description: While sightseeing at the Geyser Gulch National Park, the Tennyson trio uncover Steam Smythe's steam-powered generator and must shut it down before it overloads the power grid or, even worse, causes a massive earthquake that destroys the entire park!
